    "lyricsTelugu": "పాట రచయిత:",
    "lyricsEnglish": "Lyricist:\n\nEnglish LyricsAudioChords\n\nRandi Yehovaanu Goorchi\n\nUthsaaha Gaanamu Chesedamu (2)\n\nAayane Mana Poshakudu\n\nNammdagina Devudani (2)\n\nNammdagina Devudani\n\nAaha… Hallelujah Aaha Hallelujah\n\nKashta Nashtamulennunnaa\n\nPongu Saagaraaledurainaa (2)\n\nAayane Mana Aashrayam\n\nIrukulu Ibbandulalo (2)\n\nIrukulu Ibbandulalo      ||Randi||\n\nVirigi Naligna Hrudayamutho\n\nDeva Devuni Sannidhilo (2)\n\nAnishamu Praardhinchina\n\nKalugu Eevulu Manakenno (2)\n\nKalugu Eevulu Manakenno     ||Randi||\n\nThrova Thappina Vaaralanu\n\nCheradeese Naadhudani (2)\n\nNeethi Sooryundaayane Ani\n\nNithyamu Sthuthi Cheyudamu (2)\n\nNithyamu Sthuthi Cheyudamu     ||Randi||\n\nRandi Yehovaanu Gurchi Uthsaaha Gaanamu Chesedamu\nAayane Mana Poshakudu Nammdagina Devudani (2)\nNammdagina Devudani\nAaha… Hallelujah Aaha Hallelujah\n\nKashta Nashtamulennunna Pongu Sagaraleduraina (2)\nAayane Mana Aashayamu Irukulu Ibbandulalo (2) ||Randi||\n\nVirigi Naligna Hrudayamutho Devadevuni Sannidhini\nAnishamu Prardhinchina Kalugu Eevalu Manakennno (2)||Randi||\n\nTrova Tappina Varalanu Cheradise Naadhudani\nNeeti Sooryudayanenani Nithyamu Stuti Cheyudamu (2)||Randi||\n\njQuery(function() {jQuery( \"#tabs_16599_0\" ).posttabs({ tabname : \"tabs_16599_0\",\t\t\t\t\tfade \t: \"0\",\t\t\t\t\tactive\t: \"\",\t\t\t\t\treload\t: \"0\",\t\t\t\t\tnav\t: \"0\",\t\t\t\t\tnexttext: \"Next »\",\t\t\t\t\tprevtext: \"« Prev\",\t\t\t\t\tenablecookie:\"1\"\t\t\t\t});})"
